Module kivakit.core
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.time

Class DayOfWeek

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.time.BaseTime<DayOfWeek>
com.telenav.kivakit.core.time.DayOfWeek
All Implemented Interfaces:
DoubleQuantizable, Quantizable, Stringable, StringSource, PointInTime<DayOfWeek,Duration>, TimeMeasurement, Comparable<PointInTime<?,?>>
public class DayOfWeek extends BaseTime<DayOfWeek>
Typesafe value for day of week. Supports both ISO and Java ordinals.

Creation

  • isoDayOfWeek(int) - Constructs from an ISO day of the week (0-6)
  • javaDayOfWeek(int) - Constructs from a Java day of the week (1-7)
  • javaDayOfWeek(java.time.DayOfWeek) - Constructs from a Java day of the week

Conversions

  • asDay() - Converts to a Day object
  • asIsoOrdinal() - The ISO number for this day of the week, from 0 to 6
  • asJavaOrdinal() - The Java number for this day of the week, from 1 to 7
  • asJavaDayOfWeek() - This day of the week as a Java day of the week object
Author:
jonathanl (shibo), matthieun
